<abstract><t>This draft defines the User-group Aware Policy Control (UAPC) framework, which facilitates consistent enforcement of security policies based on user group identity.  Policies are used to control security policy enforcement using a policy server and a security controller.  Northbound APIs are also discussed.</t></abstract>

